ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSanDisk-MicroSDXC-Memory-Nintendo-Switch%2Fdp%2FB07QD6R5L7">256GB 型号</a>。它们已经过系统专门测试，因此您知道它们可以无缝工作。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> 8Bitdo Pro 2</h2><p><core-commerce id="054a1e9386f941799dba0c4cb649a2f9" data-type="product-list"></p><p> OLED Switch 背面的支架得到了改进，现在在桌面模式下玩游戏变得更加容易。但你仍然使用相同的旧 Joy-Con 控制器，这对于手较大的玩家来说可能有点太小了。在这种情况下，您将需要升级到更专业级的游戏手柄。是的，还有<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwMU5BV0tZWjA_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZTMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQxMzY0NTg2LTk0YjYtNDBjNC1iZjc4LTg5Y2Q3NjA0MTNkMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZ2jWjz8OlWJXyLNLbMGCVXA5L7EMnZop_G0zr4NACc8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB01NAWKYZ0">任天堂的 Pro 控制器</a>，如果你能买到的话，它仍然是你的 Switch 整体的最佳选择，但<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9XaXJlbGVzcy1CbHVldG9vdGgtQ29udHJvbGxlci1Kb3lzdGlja3MtVmlicmF0aW9uL2RwL0IwODVTVFI5UjM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZTMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQxMzY0NTg2LTk0YjYtNDBjNC1iZjc4LTg5Y2Q3NjA0MTNkMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAVwsS9aljhRkKMyxAkv9EmgDPRkTG3eBZGvhPMTn2I9a&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FWireless-Bluetooth-Controller-Joysticks-Vibration%2Fdp%2FB085STR9R3">8Bitdo 的 Pro 2</a>也很棒，更不用说难以置信的灵活性了；您可以将其与 Android 设备以及 PC 或 Mac 桌面一起使用。而且它比任天堂制造的选项便宜 20 美元。</p><h2> 8Bitdo Lite 2</h2><p><core-commerce id="16e4195c328347ce8079ee495a82851a" data-type="product-list"></p><p>虽然官方<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwMU5BV0tZWjA_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZTMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQxMzY0NTg2LTk0YjYtNDBjNC1iZjc4LTg5Y2Q3NjA0MTNkMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZ2jWjz8OlWJXyLNLbMGCVXA5L7EMnZop_G0zr4NACc8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB01NAWKYZ0">Pro 控制器</a>和 Pro 2 都是功能齐全的游戏手柄，但它们的尺寸并不小。当你的包里没有太多空间但需要比 Joy-Con 稍大一点的东西来玩时，这会在旅途中带来很大的不同。在这种情况下，我推荐<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9CbHVldG9vdGgtR2FtZXBhZC1SYXNwYmVycnktVHVycXVvaXNlLUdhbWluZy1Db25zb2xlL2RwL0IwQjNESDFaNFA_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZTMtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImQxMzY0NTg2LTk0YjYtNDBjNC1iZjc4LTg5Y2Q3NjA0MTNkMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAZjG_ehwUfW2fNJvRzqnVxkKew_cGxXf1CqpXM4O1DmC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBluetooth-Gamepad-Raspberry-Turquoise-Gaming-Console%2Fdp%2FB0B3DH1Z4P">8Bitdo Lite 2</a> ，它提供了一个真正的方向键，以及两个操纵杆、肩部触发器，甚至运动控制，因此您不会放弃任何功能。它的颜色编码与 Switch Lite 相匹配，但这并不意味着它不是 Switch OLED 的可靠伴侣。 （如果您是 2D 爱好者，您可能想尝试一下<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-029