 Xbox 游戏玩家来说， <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfH9RFAHDlup4HahzlvHnljKxq_TveN6s253x6X9jd8V&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElite-2-Controller-Black-Xbox-One%2Fdp%2FB07SFKTLZM">微软的第二代 Elite 游戏手柄</a>是最好的控制器之一，并且值得投资。它具有可更换的拇指杆、后部按钮和舒适的握把。更不用说，它是少数可以通过 USB-C 充电的 Xbox 游戏手柄之一。</p><p>如果您对玩老游戏更感兴趣，或者只是在寻找不同风格的控制器，我们也是<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhYWThIOUQ1P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWR5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4YTYxNzVmOS1iYjljLTQwNDgtOTExOS1kNGM2ZWI1NGFhMTQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQ_zTGagtXKT9a09Z0S7Kpg4xkGyaVbWU48P3TAn4ohK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08XY8H9D5">八位堂 Pro 2</a>的忠实粉丝。它非常舒适，其方向垫是市场上最好的方向垫之一。它还为 PC 游戏提供了出色的控制器（尽管任何最新的 Xbox 控制器也可以通过蓝牙在计算机上运行）。</p> <a class="athena-button rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=shopnow-button&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATyaZE6kpTG4yf_fMRbXPYxDL2G1C3rJ6j91aLZ5gLm3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElite-2-Controller-Black-Xbox-One%2Fdp%2FB07SFKTLZM" id="78fca88108fb420d8722f299bab7ac9c" data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1">在亚马逊购买 Elite 游戏手柄 - 180 美元</a><a class="athena-button rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=shopnow-button&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhYWThIOUQ1P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWR6LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI4YTYxNzVmOS1iYjljLTQwNDgtOTExOS1kNGM2ZWI1NGFhMTQifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAcal10ne1vxkvC9DfDrapnzSTDBgzVwgM_lICcmZwxZT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08XY8H9D5" id="d0393efe1166441bb9fc82c133dfdeba" data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1">在亚马逊购买 8Bitdo Pro 2 - 50 美元</a><h2>专用控制器再次酷炫！</h2><p><core-commerce id="3edd842c738e48e6a73b9a19fd2f58f5" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您玩《微软模拟飞行》足够长的时间，您就会意识到使用标准游戏手柄只能玩到此为止。是时候使用飞行棒了！在与飞行模拟器狂热分子讨论并阅读大量评论后，我们建议您使用<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVZq7udkvgOyemQpdGVPkQdzCUp4xVH8JywxvJtn1XIp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FThrustmaster-T-Flight-Hotas-One-xbox%2Fdp%2FB07643TW2V">Thrustmaster 的 T-Flight Hotas One 操纵杆</a>。它提供逼真的五轴控制、14 个按钮和一个可拆卸的油门。与一些笨重的 PC 解决方案不同，它足够紧凑，可以放在咖啡桌或膝上办公桌上。 （如果您愿意，也可以在计算机上使用它。）</p><p>如果您更喜欢汽车， <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAROswsx-L4CbIRm6EzHNaQ_UVJy75PooUKZm0Kn9UFDU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-G923-Racing-Wheel-PS4%2Fdp%2FB07PFB72NL">罗技的 G923 赛车方向盘</a>给我们留下了深刻的印象。将其添加到您的游戏设置中，它会感觉就像一个<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/logitech-g923-racing-wheel-hands-on-070115330.html">真正的方向盘</a>，具有舒适的握感、钢质换挡拨片和三个坚固的踏板。一旦它被夹在桌子上，它就会提供令人惊讶的真实驾驶体验 - 更好地在《极限竞速：地平线 5》中穿越墨西哥。它的价格绝对昂贵，为 400 美元，但它是一项高质量的投资，可以持续用于许多即将推出的赛车游戏。</p> <a class="athena-button rapid-with-clickid" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=shopnow-button&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbZ_A7wmC1z3mPLaW_UVGlwO5hmh8Ew_Zc5PzeQ7Wy9G&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-G923-Racing-Wheel-PS4%2Fdp%2FB07PFB72NL" id="93ed012348734086bcb27f245efe3550" data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1">在亚马逊购买罗技赛车方向盘 - 400 美元</a><h2>增加你的存储空间</h2><p><core-commerce id="8c90ca7d306d40ad83b5256a75859c18" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您足够幸运，在推出时获得了新的 Xbox Series X 或 S，那么您很可能已经熟悉它们的存储限制。幸运的是，您可以使用<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TZWFnYXRlLVN0b3JhZ2UtRXhwYW5zaW9uLVNvbGlkLVN0YXRlL2RwL0IwOEszUzZXSk0_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZHktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjhhNjE3NWY5LWJiOWMtNDA0OC05MTE5LWQ0YzZlYjU0YWExNCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQxxbKcgDifcqPMO23L3T4veGdUViqi_H7NkGm56aYRM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSeagate-Storage-Expansion-Solid-State%2Fdp%2FB08K3S6WJM">希捷的存储扩展卡</a>之一轻松地给自己更多的喘息空间，这些扩展卡的速度与游戏机内的高速 SSD 一样快。除了发布时推出的 1TB 卡外，希捷最近还推出了 512GB 和 2TB 选项。目前我们建议选择 1TB，但如果您能负担得起，2TB SSD 的使用寿命肯定会更长。</p><p>您还可以通过 USB 将传统的外部硬盘驱动器（例如<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdlmswe_1em-sQjCduul8uujJDz6kNGoEBqlh-j6_sFP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSeagate-Game-Drive-Green-STEA2000403%2Fdp%2FB01065S79E">Seagate 的 2TB Game Drive）</a>连接到 Xbox Series X 和 S。它们的速度太慢，无法全速运行当前游戏，但它们可以以便宜得多的价格为您提供大量存储空间。它们对于玩初代 Xbox 和 360 上的游戏非常有用。它们还可以用作“冷存储”，以释放宝贵的 SSD 上的空间。较新的游戏可以轻松地在这些驱动器之间来回移动，这样您就不必再次下载它们。</p><h2>调整你的声音</h2><p><core-commerce id="662051baa10a4cbbb7d1089383c44558" data-type="product-list"></p><p>您应该得到比通过糟糕的电视扬声器体验视频游戏更好的体验。 While you could just plug in whatever wired headphones you have laying around into your Xbox controller, we&#39;d recommend investing in a wireless gaming headset. They&#39;ll likely sound better, and they remove the whole cord problem entirely. The <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUReOyFD2kEaJr9t3EI7Ke_XuJK7EaPUD0p-3KQ18ipX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSteelSeries-Arctis-Wireless-Gaming-Headset-Integrated%2Fdp%2FB07RJHH6Q8">SteelSeries Arctis 9X</a> is one of the best Xbox wireless headset options around, with beefy drivers, a comfortable fit and sturdy build quality. We were <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-04-23-steelseries-arctix-9x-xbox-wireless-headphones.html">impressed during our hands-on testing,</a> as they sounded just as good as the company&#39;s excellent<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-03-13-steelseries-arctis-pro.html">Arctis Pro PC headphones</a> .</p><h2> Upgrade to a real media remote</h2><p><core-commerce id="20826dfcebd74a43941e240d57b04f0f" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Tired of controlling Netflix playback with your controller? Then pick up <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXMg65_XUr9fOYkL6adNo5Aa-h3L7qlVEgxnrA4SJh1P&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F8Bitdo-Media-Remote-Short-Infrared-x%2Fdp%2FB09B2R2GRM%3Fth%3D1">8BitDo&#39;s Media Remote</a> . Available in long and short designs (the latter removes numbers and other extraneous buttons), they&#39;re well-made remotes that fit the Xbox&#39;s clean aesthetic and, with their low price point, they&#39;re an excellent value. I&#39;ve been using the short model to control 4K Blu-rays and tons of streaming apps, and it&#39;s far easier to use than a controller when it comes to quickly fast-forwarding. Now, I don&#39;t have to put my drink down to skip to another chapter.</p><p></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-xbox-series-x-series-s-accessories-140035165.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-xbox-series-x-series-s-accessories-140035165.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8a6175f9-bb9c-4048-9119-d4c6eb54aa14</guid><dc:creator> Devindra Hardawar</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 26 Jun 2023 16:25:17 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687831954</ingested><modified> 2023-06-27T02:12:43+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Devindra Hardawar]]></category><media:content height="1281" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/830539f0-1f73-11eb-80ff-c43927b926a4" width="2000"><media:keywords> headline </media:keyw